'''Binoc droids''' were bipedal, [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] [[Droid/Legends|droids]] with extended binocular [[Photoreceptor/Legends|photoreceptors]]. They were not originally combat models, probably being designed for technical work. However, [[Z-X3|Zee-Exthree]] modified at least two such droids on [[Kligson's Moon/Legends|Kligson's Moon]] with chest [[Blaster cannon/Legends|blaster cannons]] similar to his own, for combat in his [[Kligson's Moon civil war|mutiny]].

